title: Cooking/Level up table
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Cooking/Level up table
LevelNew abilities
Each level
  • Using the Cook-o-matic 100 provides a burn chance reduction.
  • For burn rates, see the Burn Level article.
  • Using the Hosidius Kitchen and/or Cooking gauntlets provides a burn chance reduction.
  • Completing the Elite Kourend & Kebos Diary will reduce the chance to burn inside the Hosidius city kitchens by an extra 5% (making it 10% reduced burn chance)
  • For burn rates, see the Burn Level article.
